We wish to thank the government for making life a little easier for ordinary Kenyans in 2020.We were particularly happy with the recognition of young talented engineers.  Of all the years that have gone before us, 2020 is the one that will never go to heaven. Even if 2020 goes to heaven and is denied a permit to drink milk and honey, not even lawyers will volunteer to defend it.
We saw bad things last year. For the first time, staying alive featured among the top items on the bucket list of those making New Year resolutions. If you can read this, it means you have made it.



