As we wait for the government to scramble the first batch of the Covid-19 vaccine, it is our expectation that the Covid millionaires will issue a statement promising to put their conscience before their stomachs; and in the likely event they don’t, the vaccines won’t end up rotting inside go-downs as they argue on who should receive an arm or a leg and who should be content with the feathers.



